{"tid":293810,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【粵語】洛奇：拳王再臨","createTime":"2017-06-22T12:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T14:06:08.000Z","uid":69384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15c0b31df9b75ac3b9d6bd4ad05a1db33022243b","tid":293810,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/57b9a354cc418d28fac78c7f5e8349ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F57b9a354cc418d28fac78c7f5e8349ca.jpg&h=1a8ff6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>主台:</strong><a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/chicktv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fchicktv&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1ea0b08a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/chicktv</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">專頁:</span></strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nikuniku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnikuniku&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=9e5fa788\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/nikuniku</a><br />\n<br />\n早已退隱、闊別拳壇多年的拳王洛奇，妻子不幸離世，加上與自己非常疼愛的獨生兒子關係疏離，只好全心寄情於自己經營的餐廳。憑昔日的名氣，餐廳客似雲來，當中大部份到來光顧的客人都是慕名而來。洛奇每天就是在餐廳裡與客人回顧往事及忙於拍照應酬，生活平淡如水‥‥<br />\n<br />\n當今世界拳壇最強的重量級冠軍迪臣，以非凡技巧打遍天下無敵手，剩下的只有曾是拳王的洛奇一人最有實力與他一比高下﹗本著對拳壇的熱誠及給兒子作個好榜樣的出發點，洛奇便一口答應接受挑戰。一場世紀拳賽迅即成為注目焦點─是身懷絕技的新霸主迪遜更勝一籌，還是滿腔熱情的舊拳王洛奇爆冷？誰勝誰負....是時候來個最後了結！"},{"pid":"cc910c5f4b373df54df2f5cde38c396d06b8eb54","tid":293810,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083c38f89fb7c06894ca7afaf0cb80a86d732d3e","tid":293810,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cf61318d11d156803fe99603ea4ca42d217287","tid":293810,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a8b60df187d7ebd92e7afdf5133ed218574caf","tid":293810,"uid":69384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}